Dj Mbale The programming manager at Star FM always has a handful when she is dealing with the energy of DJ Mbale. Yet today being his birthday, the entire team at the nation’s favourite station can look back with ride and be thankful that Mbale was hatched at all! Turning 31 today, DJ Mbale is one of the hottest, youngest and freshest voice to have emerged from the musical revolution that Star FM has touched. Many Happy returns to the bubbly Mbale from Star FM and The Saturday Herald!  